\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 15. P. sieberi} Sprengel, {\i Pugillus}{\b  1}: 15 (1813). Like {\b 13} but upper cauline leaves sessile, ovate-lanceolate to ovate; bracts ovate, acuminate, acutely serrate; stigmas 3. 2n = 20.{\i  Rocky and stony slopes; calcicole. • S.E. Alps.} Au It Ju.
\par 

